[],"root":false,"id":184,"parent_node_name":"hardware"},"member":{"id":490892,"username":"helee9199","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/helee9199","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5a82249defccd648ef6d961847c0480c?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5a82249defccd648ef6d961847c0480c?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5a82249defccd648ef6d961847c0480c?s=73&d=retro","created":1590129759,"last_modified":1654649047},"last_reply_by":"n666us","last_touched":1654653666,"title":"macbook 使用无线鼠标 感觉粘粘的 不跟手","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/858058","created":1654649139,"deleted":0,"content":"mbp 2021 m1 14'。\r\n用的是 anywhere3 就是拖动的时候就感觉有一丢丢延迟，有种粘滞感。\r\n而且很容易晃出大鼠标。\r\n但是用有线的 就很顺溜。同样晃的频率和幅度也不那么容易出现大鼠标。\r\n连接方式是蓝牙连接。\r\n到底是什么情况。有解么？","content_rendered":"<p>mbp 2021 m1 14'。\n用的是 anywhere3 就是拖动的时候就感觉有一丢丢延迟，有种粘滞感。\n而且很容易晃出大鼠标。\n但是用有线的 就很顺溜。同样晃的频率和幅度也不那么容易出现大鼠标。\n连接方式是蓝牙连接。\n到底是什么情况。有解么？</p>\n","last_modified":1654649139,"replies":13,"id":858058},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_large.png?m=1650127281","name":"share","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_normal.png?m=1650127281","title":"分享发现","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/share","topics":35590,"footer":"","header":"分享你看到的好玩的，有信息量的，欢迎从这里获取灵感。","title_alternative":"Share","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1650127281","stars":4852,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":16,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":36118,"username":"coolair","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/coolair","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4fe/52ac/36118_mini.png?m=1642386161","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4fe/52ac/36118_normal.png?m=1642386161","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4fe/52ac/36118_large.png?m=1642386161","created":1363654688,"last_modified":1642386161},"last_reply_by":"Issacx","last_touched":1654674997,"title":"大家到“数码荔枝”购买产品的时候请擦亮眼睛","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/858183","created":1654670746,"deleted":0,"content":"刚刚到“数码荔枝”购买了两个软件，其中一个图片搜索软件看上去很符合我的需求，然后想也没想就直接下单了。\r\n下单完成后，跳转到官网下载，才发现这个软件的最后一次更新日期竟然是 2018 年……\r\n\r\n另外，我看了下官网的其他软件以及 Facebook ，更新日期都停留在了 2018 年。\r\n\r\n想必作者是放弃他所有软件的维护了。\r\n\r\n不怪“数码荔枝”未对此做说明，找了客服想退款，被告知“虚拟产品提货后不支持退哈”。\r\n\r\n也罢，怪自己下单前没仔细调研，好在目前还能用，就是别指望 Bug 修复之类的了。\r\n\r\n大家以后购买软件产品时一定要擦亮眼睛，别买到已经寿终正寝的产品。","content_rendered":"<p>刚刚到“数码荔枝”购买了两个软件，其中一个图片搜索软件看上去很符合我的需求，然后想也没想就直接下单了。\n下单完成后，跳转到官网下载，才发现这个软件的最后一次更新日期竟然是 2018 年……</p>\n<p>另外，我看了下官网的其他软件以及 Facebook ，更新日期都停留在了 2018 年。</p>\n<p>想必作者是放弃他所有软件的维护了。</p>\n<p>不怪“数码荔枝”未对此做说明，找了客服想退款，被告知“虚拟产品提货后不支持退哈”。</p>\n<p>也罢，怪自己下单前没仔细调研，好在目前还能用，就是别指望 Bug 修复之类的了。</p>\n<p>大家以后购买软件产品时一定要擦亮眼睛，别买到已经寿终正寝的产品。</p>\n","last_modified":1654670746,"replies":12,"id":858183},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913","name":"apple","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913","title":"Apple","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","topics":18631,"footer":"","header":"设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。","title_alternative":"Apple","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","stars":2184,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":184,"parent_node_name":"hardware"},"member":{"id":551213,"username":"Wooork","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Wooork","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/928f108b28a8997180fcc3e4d199cb3f?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/928f108b28a8997180fcc3e4d199cb3f?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"http